Package: healthdata.gov
Title: HealthData.gov (HHS) Socrata API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the HealthData.gov Socrata open data portal from HHS.
    Access 127 datasets covering COVID-19 hospital capacity, testing, treatments, child welfare,
    and HHS governance data. Includes LLM context injection via hd_context().
